# Blood and Sand

## Project Description
Blood and Sand is a web-based game that I am building as a passion project to learn web technologies. The game features an engaging storyline, interactive gameplay, and a modern design to provide an immersive experience for players.

## Features
- Responsive design
- Interactive gameplay elements
- User authentication
- Dynamic content
- SEO optimization

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- Tailwind CSS
- JavaScript
- Next.js
- Node.js
- Express.js
- Firebase

## Installation
1. Clone the repository:
    ```
    git clone https://github.com/yourusername/blood-and-sand.git
    ```
2. Navigate to the project directory:
    ```
    cd blood-and-sand
    ```
3. Install dependencies:
    ```
    npm install
    ```

## Usage
1. Start the development server:
    ```
    npm start
    ```
2. Open your browser and navigate to `http://localhost:3000`

